reviews.text: On May 3, 2019, I bumped into here for a lunch set (Bill $128) as there was no problem for me to get a seat. The warm bread, salad and soup came quickly to meet my empty stomach but for the main course brought by the captain after my urge landed on my table at 13:50. Although I had to consume it and was late to return to the office, I still tipped them as I should have realised that it was not a fast food chain！
Very good lunch. The fish is perfect
The food is ok service is acceptable, I would go back to eat here, though wine selection is poor and they may not have the one you want on the menu, steak is tasty and all over a good meal.

good service
pricy and food is only fair
Teate of steak , other food and beer are so good....

result.name: Outback Steakhouse

reviews.text: 慢燒牛👍👍👍👍

最差既outback。
一，食物求其， 味道差，賣相差。成八舊水個套餐，大約係二百既享受。意粉同沙律真係得啖笑，麵包正常，扒就勉強接受到。
二，侍應和著白色恤衫的主管都係嬉皮笑臉，三五成群。
三，服務，似茶餐廳咁，匆匆忙忙，粗粗魯魯。一俾錢，兩三個侍應好似洒樓咁 呯呤嘭唥執野。

Blacklisted.
貴，但又好大份。前菜（歺包）好好味。

食物質素 越來越差
服務更差 主菜來了 忘記給予醬汁
問了5 個 員工 等了超過15 分鐘
到發脾氣了 才有一位員工 即時拿過來
可牛扒都冷了
職員親切友善,任坐任傾,敘舊吹水一流😁

reviews.text: Vast selection of baby related merchandise, Parents favorite. A huge supermarket sits next to this department store as well. A true one stop shop for families
Huge mall, connected to other shopping as well.  Good transportation options in and out.
Great place for shopping, especially for beauty products! Family mall with everything you need.

Central location. Linked to 5 or 6 other shopping arcades. Linked to the subway line at Tuen Mun station. Many car parks, and some offer free parking with purchase. I'm happy with this place as I'm always able to find whatever I'm looking for here. Finding my car after getting parking ticket stamped is always a challenge tho.
This is the closest to home and what you get.ftom.anywhere, you get it here  mostly, why ho anywhere else. My kids are practical, when they are here, they love it just here.
